<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
  Lusik & Sons sitemap.
  Served from the repo root and referenced in robots.txt.

  When you add a new journal post:
    1. Add a new <url> block below, copying the format of the
       existing journal entries.
    2. Set <lastmod> to today's date in YYYY-MM-DD.
    3. Commit + push; the next deploy makes the new URL crawlable.

  When you add a new product or category to src/data/catalog.js:
    1. Add a <url> block under the matching /shop section below.
    2. The slug must match the entry's `slug` field in catalog.js.
    3. Live products get priority 0.8, placeholders 0.5 — they're
       not buyable yet so we don't want them ranking ahead of the
       real ones.
-->
